Class Vehicle

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.Vehicle

  • public class Vehicle
extends java.lang.Object
    Vehicle class stores the details of a particular vehicle such as its capacity, count of vehicles of a particular type, etc.
    Author:
    Abhishek Joshi, Anand Tirthgirikar, Sandesh Prabhu
